features.name: Sharm Luli, in front of wadi el-Gamal islands, this place has been taken for Myos Hormos because of Strabo's description, but Pliny mentions Iambe insula between Myos Hormos and Berenike. Jacotin (1809) calls it Sharm el-Koman. Belzoni (1822:328) calls the island Gambe.
